        "highlight": "Once upon a time",
        "keywords": "emperor, liked clothes",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "p1_1",
            "text": "He wanted to buy some new clothes.",
            "emoji": "🛍️",
            "keywords": "buy, new clothes",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "p2",
        "text": "Two brothers came and lied to him, 'We can make wonderful clothes!'",
        "emoji": "👨‍👦",
        "keywords": "brothers, lied, wonderful clothes",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "p2_1",
            "text": "'But only clever people can see them!'",
            "emoji": "🧠",
            "highlight": "But",
            "keywords": "only clever, see them",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "p2_2",
            "text": "They pretended to make the clothes.",
            "emoji": "🎭",
            "keywords": "pretended, make clothes",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "p3",
        "text": "The emperor's officials couldn't see the clothes, but they said, 'What lovely clothes!'",
        "emoji": "👨‍💼",
        "highlight": "but",
        "keywords": "officials, couldn't see, said lovely",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "p3_1",
            "text": "The emperor couldn't see anything either, but he said, 'They're beautiful!'",
            "emoji": "🙈",
            "highlight": "either, but",
            "keywords": "emperor couldn't see, said beautiful",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "p3_2",
            "text": "No one wanted to look silly.",
            "emoji": "🤫",
            "keywords": "No one, look silly",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "p4",
        "text": "The emperor decided to show everyone his new clothes.",
        "emoji": "🚶",
        "keywords": "emperor, show everyone",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "p4_1",
            "text": "People in the street praised them.",
            "emoji": "👏",
            "keywords": "People, praised them",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "p4_2",
            "text": "They were afraid to look silly too!",
